name: com.ageoflearning.kraken-ioc
description:
This is a Unity package of KrakenIoc, a publicly-available Dependency Injection (DI) library in C#, created originally by Age of Learning.
The original Git repo is available at https://github.com/AgeOfLearning/kraken-ioc

Check the changelog for version equivalents between this Unity package and the original pure C# KrakenIoc APIs.
